arts.ttl: Caen fans protest Mbappé ownership: 'Not a toy'
arts.sum: Fans of French second division side SM Caen made their feelings about part-owner Kylian Mbappé clear on Friday, unfurling several banners during their 1-0 defeat to Clermont Foot.

arts.ttl: Caen fans hang banners against club owner Kylian Mbappé
